h4=A.hu(A.b([A.cn("Kerala's largest waterfall, thundering through rainforest.","55 km from Kochi","Athirappilly Falls"),A.cn("Home of the endangered Nilgiri tahr and rolling shola grasslands.",b1,"Eravikulam National Park"),A.cn("An undeveloped fishing coast of coconut palms and quiet sand.","15 km from Alleppey","Marari Beach")],i2),"September \u2013 March",h1,d,6,h9,!0,h3,h0,h5,i1,"d01",h8,h7,9.4981,76.3388,"Kerala",5,"Kerala unfolds slowly \u2014 a latticework of palm-shaded canals, spice-scented hills and beaches the colour of raw silk. Drift through Alleppey aboard a private kettuvallam houseboat, wake to mist rolling over Munnar's tea terraces, and end each evening with Kathakali fire and coastal seafood. This is India at its most unhurried, curated down to the last cardamom pod.",24500,4.9,1284,A.b([A.dz("Ananya Iyer","The houseboat evening alone was worth the trip. Aurevia thought of everything \u2014 even the playlist on board matched the sunset.",b3,b2,5),A.dz("James & Clara Whitmore","Our honeymoon was flawless. The plantation bungalow in Munnar felt like a film set, and our host Vipin was extraordinary.",b4,"London",5),A.dz("Rohit Menon","Took my parents and my kids \u2014 every generation found something to love. Seamless logistics.",b5,"Mumbai",4.5)],i3),"Private houseboats, plantation stays and Ayurvedic rituals. Curated 6-day Kerala journeys by Aurevia.","Kerala Luxury Tour Packages \u2014 Backwaters, Munnar & Kochi","kerala","Where the backwaters keep their own time",h4,a3)
