h3=A.hu(A.b([A.cn("The storied gateway to Lahaul, snowbound most of the year.","51 km from Manali","Rohtang Pass"),A.cn("A fifteenth-century timber castle above the Kullu valley.","21 km from Manali","Naggar Castle"),A.cn("Sulphur springs beside an ancient stone temple.","3 km from Manali","Vashisht hot springs")],i2),"March \u2013 June, October \u2013 February",h8,d,5,h1,!1,o,q,i1,n,"d05",h9,p,32.2396,77.1887,"Manali",4,"Old Manali's orchards and the Kullu valley's deodar forests make the Himalaya feel domestic and wild at once. We base you in a riverside lodge, send you paragliding over Solang, trekking to Jogini falls, and \u2014 in season \u2014 through the Atal tunnel to the stark beauty of Sissu and the Lahaul valley.",16500,4.6,1108,A.b([A.dz("Sneha Kulkarni","Perfect long weekend. The lodge was gorgeous and the Sissu day felt like another planet.","October 2025","Nagpur",4.6),A.dz("Dhruv Kapoor","Paragliding was superbly organised. Great valley knowledge.",e3,"Chandigarh",4.5)],i3),"Paragliding, cedar forests and the Atal tunnel to Lahaul. Curated Manali escapes by Aurevia.","Manali Getaways \u2014 Solang, Sissu & Riverside Lodges","manali","Cedar forests, river mornings, mountain air",h3,e1)
